122:9<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">13. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"124504\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 124504)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(124504)\">1 Cor. 5:5<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"124505\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 124505)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(124505)\">1 Tim. 1:20<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"124506\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 124506)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(124506)\">Alma 37:15<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"115310\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 115310)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(115310)\">D&amp;C 104:9-10<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"124503\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 124503)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(124503)\">Moses 5:23<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">14. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"109816\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 109816)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(109816)\">Eph. 4:30<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"113839\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 113839)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(113839)\">D&amp;C 45:17<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"114562\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 114562)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(114562)\">D&amp;C 78:12<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"114593\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 114593)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(114593)\">D&amp;C 82:21<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"116051\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 116051)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(116051)\">D&amp;C 124:124<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"116393\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 116393)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(116393)\">D&amp;C 132:26<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">15. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"114162\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 114162)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(114162)\">D&amp;C 63:15<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">16. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"111227\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 111227)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(111227)\">2 Ne. 15:1<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"112446\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 112446)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(112446)\">Hel. 5:47<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"116067\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 116067)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(116067)\">D&amp;C 126:1<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">17. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"113911\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 113911)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(113911)\">D&amp;C 46:14<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"114726\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 114726)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(114726)\">D&amp;C 84:80<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"115359\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 115359)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(115359)\">D&amp;C 105:18<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"115536\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 115536)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(115536)\">D&amp;C 108:5<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n  <\/div>\n<\/div>"}